1911年冬天，在美国的一家大医院里，一位患尿毒症的病人已经昏迷了好几天，情况十分危急。虽然医生已经奋力抢救了，但病人最后还是停止了心跳。 <img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmIRg4AMQGZ0F52PuyvPRg8BTeTBWaPZyaexBM8kjnuAOPvia07F42TtQ/0" data-ratio="1.0395256916996047" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmIRg4AMQGZ0F52PuyvPRg8BTeTBWaPZyaexBM8kjnuAOPvia07F42TtQ/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" /><br />
抢救病人的年轻医生名叫爱贝尔，他善良而有责任心，病人的死让他十分难过。<br />
<img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmX82iahLcYTtJk4yqo6aPCOSesF6ianNoS2jByX80FRN3uq4BPZgTXkIg/0" data-ratio="0.6679841897233202" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmX82iahLcYTtJk4yqo6aPCOSesF6ianNoS2jByX80FRN3uq4BPZgTXkIg/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
代替尿毒症患者已失去正常功能的肾脏来工作。<br />
<img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmKsXauUwHkXjPkCbOnlPrGFXTxOu987YD96YQO5I6R129hN1naOquTQ/0" data-ratio="0.4209486166007905" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmKsXauUwHkXjPkCbOnlPrGFXTxOu987YD96YQO5I6R129hN1naOquTQ/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" /> <br />
要将这个想法变成现实可不容易，需要解决许多问题。肾脏最基本的功能就是将血液里的各种新陈代谢的废物过滤出来，形成尿液。  <img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmaibxN7GHJmRiaibTsNjoOYERooX2WbbhMCzYTbFuehFdDzQiaH5qia0MOBg/0" data-ratio="0.5928853754940712" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmaibxN7GHJmRiaibTsNjoOYERooX2WbbhMCzYTbFuehFdDzQiaH5qia0MOBg/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
在肾脏里有一层奇妙的滤过膜，能像筛子一样过滤废物。造人工&ldquo;肾脏&rdquo;，首先就要造出一个这样的膜。  <img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmks32GxsPFzibmibQwsP4haZFFbzSPFiacIy6iaqnsMeZ0aFWB0zAoSorhw/0" data-ratio="0.5632411067193676" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmks32GxsPFzibmibQwsP4haZFFbzSPFiacIy6iaqnsMeZ0aFWB0zAoSorhw/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
爱贝尔将业余时间都花在了寻找滤过膜上。可他搜集到的薄膜要么&ldquo;筛孔&rdquo;太小，连废物也无法通过；要么&ldquo;筛孔&rdquo;太大，大得把血液里的红细胞、蛋白质等都漏出去。  <img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmDcHGZibqx8jyqXNxSNU1AvVfcUicgeicYNaAp0dTxicib2UwpibZKFFa0Sgg/0" data-ratio="0.44861660079051385" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmDcHGZibqx8jyqXNxSNU1AvVfcUicgeicYNaAp0dTxicib2UwpibZKFFa0Sgg/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
正当他的实验陷入困境时，一位同行给他提供了由火棉胶制成的薄膜。<br />
<img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmJ4dLkbHHNf5H6BlFabnqdJ82tzRNdtYn6FcvbpKnSTlJ2VOkqsUnKg/0" data-ratio="0.5395256916996047" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmJ4dLkbHHNf5H6BlFabnqdJ82tzRNdtYn6FcvbpKnSTlJ2VOkqsUnKg/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
爱贝尔将薄膜铺在漏斗上，然后再缓慢地倒入狗的血液，只见一滴滴的清液往下滴。清液中只含有尿素等废物，而不含红细胞、白细胞和蛋白质。  <img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmlWgyXgkWug8dos91UhWTbHclIuyHj8WDw7ShichflHIM613Kia8iazOwQ/0" data-ratio="0.5968379446640316" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmlWgyXgkWug8dos91UhWTbHclIuyHj8WDw7ShichflHIM613Kia8iazOwQ/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
终于找到了！爱贝尔高兴极了。在此基础上，爱贝尔于1913年发明了一种原始的人工&ldquo;肾脏<br />
<img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmQYRBAd9GoB9oaiamsP8zyZ9QCiax9Qbp4ibta0ibenOA30iafjmDIgdib0IQ/0" data-ratio="0.6304347826086957" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmQYRBAd9GoB9oaiamsP8zyZ9QCiax9Qbp4ibta0ibenOA30iafjmDIgdib0IQ/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
为了让同行们了解自己的研究进展，爱贝尔邀请医学专家观看人工&ldquo;肾脏&rdquo;在兔子身上的使用情况。实验证明，火棉胶管滤出了大量的废物。  <img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmUVozEibQ2RWxsLovxLn5geNLe6akKtgaOSPdKGz4nZfdrSWXibE5CmJw/0" data-ratio="0.5632411067193676" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmUVozEibQ2RWxsLovxLn5geNLe6akKtgaOSPdKGz4nZfdrSWXibE5CmJw/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
可是，因为血液离开人体很快就会凝结，而且血液在经过人工&ldquo;肾脏&rdquo;时需要一个类似于泵的机器保持血液流动速度。这使得人工&ldquo;肾脏&rdquo;还不能用于救助尿毒症病人。<br />
<img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmZicWe5B2wDfkaSQ81nrfUYLGicHX5uP85E4IfNJxsspiaOY54BGSSHHsw/0" data-ratio="0.5098814229249012" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmZicWe5B2wDfkaSQ81nrfUYLGicHX5uP85E4IfNJxsspiaOY54BGSSHHsw/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
1920年，医学专家研制出了一种效果良好的抗凝药物肝素。1923年，德国医学家哈斯对人工&ldquo;肾脏&rdquo;进行改进：在血液中加入一定比例的肝素，使血液不凝结，并用电动泵对过滤的血液加速。<br />
<img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmMT6TnLP4U6icwwcQS9DrI0nJJu23ILfE8bgDJ76pKib5qcxIYGOv3icxA/0" data-ratio="0.7430830039525692" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmMT6TnLP4U6icwwcQS9DrI0nJJu23ILfE8bgDJ76pKib5qcxIYGOv3icxA/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" /> <br />
哈斯将这个改进过的人工&ldquo;肾脏&rdquo;应用于生命垂危的尿毒症患者身上，结果病人转危为安。  <img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmu9nJYXnUkT8HFFjTKfMTib0YLMpuIXylKXEaQxuicgia6FmPtI9NUlvUg/0" data-ratio="0.4308300395256917" data-w="506" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmu9nJYXnUkT8HFFjTKfMTib0YLMpuIXylKXEaQxuicgia6FmPtI9NUlvUg/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" />  <br />
1943年，荷兰医学家考尔夫又对哈斯的人工&ldquo;肾脏&rdquo;做了重大改进：采用新材料作为滤过膜；加大滤过膜的面积；安装血泵。这次改进使得人工&ldquo;肾脏&rdquo;能够真正地被广泛应用，拯救了许许多多尿毒症患者的生命。<br />
<img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmqPWNEnChNbCFXiatNFVkHgK6xk3PfoD7SDXzJSqclvDqomB5n5aJl8Q/0" data-ratio="1.0800821355236139" data-w="487" data-s="300,640" width="auto" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ePs0K02fzECAMKEibhzK6GKiaqp08865tmqPWNEnChNbCFXiatNFVkHgK6xk3PfoD7SDXzJSqclvDqomB5n5aJl8Q/640?tp=webp.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" alt="" /></div>